# Invocation & error handling

## Three invocation models

- **Synchronous** — caller waits (API GW, ALB, Function URL). **No auto-retry** — error to caller
- **Asynchronous** — Lambda queues, returns now (S3, SNS, EventBridge). **2 retries** → DLQ / Destination
- **Poll** (event source mapping) — Lambda polls in **batches** (SQS, Kinesis, DynamoDB Streams). Ordering per source

## Async failure paths

- **Dead Letter Queue** — failed payload → SQS/SNS (payload only)
- **Destinations** — success *and* failure → SQS/SNS/EventBridge/Lambda (full event + response)

## Poll failures

Retry until the record expires · **partial batch response** reports only the failed records.
